---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { PROCEDURE_CATALOG, PROCEDURE_PILLAR_SUMMARIES } from '../data/procedure-catalog';
---

<Layout
  title="시술 안내"
  description="에스리본 클리닉 시술 안내 — EBD·주사·경구약·외용제를 영역별로 정리했습니다."
>
  <div class="proc-page">
    <header class="proc-hero">
      <p class="proc-hero-badge">Treatments</p>
      <h1 class="proc-hero-title">시술 안내</h1>
      <p class="proc-hero-lead">
        블로그와 별도로, 클리닉에서 다루는 치료를 <strong>EBD(기기)</strong> · <strong>주사</strong> · <strong>경구약</strong> ·
        <strong>외용제</strong> 네 축으로 정리했습니다. 실제 시행·적응증은 내원 시 의료진이 판단합니다.
      </p>
    </header>

    <nav class="proc-toc" aria-label="시술 영역 바로가기">
      {PROCEDURE_PILLAR_SUMMARIES.map((p) => (
        <a href={`#${p.id}`} class="proc-toc-link">
          <span class="proc-toc-label">{p.label}</span>
          <span class="proc-toc-short">{p.short}</span>
        </a>
      ))}
    </nav>

    <p class="proc-disclaimer" role="note">
      아래 목록은 <strong>의학적 정보 안내용 분류</strong>이며, 모든 항목이 본원에서 시행된다는 뜻은 아닙니다. 약물·시술은 부작용·금기가 있을 수 있으니
      반드시 진료를 통해 결정합니다.
    </p>

    <p class="proc-tree-hint">
      <span class="proc-tree-hint-icon" aria-hidden="true">◇</span>
      제목 줄을 누르면 세부 분류와 항목이 차례로 펼쳐집니다. 처음엔 한 축씩 열어 보셔도 좋아요.
    </p>

    <div class="proc-tree-toolbar" role="group" aria-label="목록 펼침 제어">
      <button type="button" class="proc-tree-toggle" id="proc-tree-expand-all">
        모두 펼치기
      </button>
      <button type="button" class="proc-tree-toggle" id="proc-tree-collapse-all">
        모두 접기
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="proc-tree-root" aria-label="시술 분류 목록">
      {PROCEDURE_CATALOG.map((pillar) => (
        <section class="proc-pillar" id={pillar.id} aria-labelledby={`heading-${pillar.id}`}>
          <details class="proc-tree-branch" data-proc-branch={pillar.id}>
            <summary class="proc-tree-branch-summary">
              <span class="proc-tree-chevron" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="proc-tree-branch-text">
                <span class="proc-tree-branch-eyebrow">{pillar.subtitle}</span>
                <span class="proc-tree-branch-title" id={`heading-${pillar.id}`}>
                  {pillar.title}
                </span>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="proc-tree-branch-panel">
              <p class="proc-pillar-intro">{pillar.intro}</p>
              <div class="proc-subtree" role="group" aria-label={`${pillar.title} 하위 분류`}>
                {pillar.subgroups.map((sub) => (
                  <details class="proc-tree-leaf">
                    <summary class="proc-tree-leaf-summary">
                      <span class="proc-tree-chevron proc-tree-chevron--sm" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                      <span class="proc-tree-leaf-title">{sub.title}</span>
                    </summary>
                    <ul class="proc-item-list">
                      {sub.items.map((item) => (
                        <li>
                          <span class="proc-item-name">{item.name}</span>
                          {item.note && <span class="proc-item-note">{item.note}</span>}
                        </li>
                      ))}
                    </ul>
                  </details>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>
        </section>
      ))}
    </div>

    <footer class="proc-footer">
      <p>
        시술·약에 대한 <strong>심화 글·FAQ</strong>는 <a href="/blog/">블로그</a>에서 확인하실 수 있습니다.
      </p>
      <p>
        위치·연락은 <a href="/about#location">오시는 길</a>, 문의는 <a href="/consult">온라인 상담</a>을 이용해 주세요.
      </p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      function openBranchForHash() {
        var raw = (location.hash || '').slice(1);
        if (!raw) return;
        var id = decodeURIComponent(raw);
        var section = document.getElementById(id);
        if (!section) return;
        var branch = section.querySelector('details[data-proc-branch]');
        if (branch) branch.open = true;
        requestAnimationFrame(function () {
          section.scrollIntoView({ block: 'start', behavior: 'smooth' });
        });
      }

      function bindExpandCollapse() {
        var root = document.querySelector('.proc-tree-root');
        var expandBtn = document.getElementById('proc-tree-expand-all');
        var collapseBtn = document.getElementById('proc-tree-collapse-all');
        if (!root) return;
        if (expandBtn) {
          expandBtn.addEventListener('click', function () {
            root.querySelectorAll('details').forEach(function (d) {
              d.open = true;
            });
          });
        }
        if (collapseBtn) {
          collapseBtn.addEventListener('click', function () {
            root.querySelectorAll('details').forEach(function (d) {
              d.open = false;
            });
          });
        }
      }

      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
        bindExpandCollapse();
        openBranchForHash();
      });
      window.addEventListener('hashchange', openBranchForHash);
    })();
  </script>
</Layout>

<style>
  .proc-page {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 0 3.5rem;
    word-break: keep-all;
  }

  .proc-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3.5rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .proc-hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.3);
    color: var(--accent-dark);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .proc-hero-title {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .proc-hero-lead {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 40rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--t2);
  }

  .proc-hero-lead strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .proc-toc {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .proc-toc-link {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md, 14px);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--surface);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  }

  .proc-toc-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .proc-toc-label {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .proc-toc-short {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--t3);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .proc-disclaimer {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.15rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md, 14px);
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--t2);
  }

  .proc-tree-hint {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md, 14px);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.45);
    background: rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.06);
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--t2);
  }

  .proc-tree-hint-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--accent-dark);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .proc-tree-toolbar {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .proc-tree-toggle {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--surface);
    color: var(--text);
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  }

  .proc-tree-toggle:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--bg2);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .proc-tree-toggle:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.55);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .proc-tree-root {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.65rem;
  }

  .proc-pillar {
    scroll-margin-top: 5.5rem;
  }

  .proc-tree-branch {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg, 22px);
    background: var(--surface);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .proc-tree-branch-summary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    padding: 1.15rem 1.2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .proc-tree-branch-summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .proc-tree-branch-summary::marker {
    content: '';
  }

  .proc-tree-branch-summary:hover {
    background: var(--bg2);
  }

  .proc-tree-branch:focus-within {
    outline: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.45);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .proc-tree-chevron {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 0.55rem;
    height: 0.55rem;
    margin-top: 0.42rem;
    border-right: 2px solid var(--accent-dark);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-dark);
    transform: rotate(-45deg);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .proc-tree-chevron--sm {
    width: 0.45rem;
    height: 0.45rem;
    margin-top: 0.38rem;
    border-width: 1.5px;
  }

  .proc-tree-branch[open] > .proc-tree-branch-summary .proc-tree-chevron {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    margin-top: 0.32rem;
  }

  .proc-tree-leaf[open] > .proc-tree-leaf-summary .proc-tree-chevron {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    margin-top: 0.28rem;
  }

  .proc-tree-branch-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .proc-tree-branch-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent-dark);
  }

  .proc-tree-branch-title {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .proc-tree-branch-panel {
    padding: 0 1.2rem 1.2rem 2.35rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .proc-pillar-intro {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1rem 0 1.1rem;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--t2);
    max-width: 48rem;
  }

  .proc-subtree {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .proc-tree-leaf {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md, 14px);
    background: var(--surface);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .proc-tree-leaf-summary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.4;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .proc-tree-leaf-summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .proc-tree-leaf-summary::marker {
    content: '';
  }

  .proc-tree-leaf-summary:hover {
    background: var(--bg2);
  }

  .proc-tree-leaf-title {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .proc-item-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0 1rem 1rem 1.85rem;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding-top: 0.85rem;
    background: var(--surface);
  }

  .proc-item-list li {
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--t2);
    padding-left: 0.65rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-gold-light);
  }

  .proc-item-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .proc-item-note {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--t3);
  }

  .proc-footer {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--t2);
  }

  .proc-footer a {
    color: var(--accent-dark);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 0.15em;
  }

  .proc-footer p {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .proc-footer p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .proc-toc {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .proc-tree-branch-panel {
      padding-left: 1.15rem;
      padding-right: 1rem;
    }

    .proc-item-list {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
